reviewText:
This is a great DVD of vintage Ub Iwerks animation.

Valiant Tailor (1934) aka The King's Tailor
Three Bears (1935)
Dick Whittington's Cat (1936)
Little Boy Blue (1936)
Queen of Hearts (1934)
Simple Simon (1935)
Jack Frost (1934)
Famous Fairy Tales, Masquerade Holiday (1934) aka Hell's Fire
